{"title":"用 QtConcurrent 防止界面假死","date":"2016-10-09T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 10, 2016","L":"10/10/2016","MM-DD":"10-10"},"link":"2016/10/10/用QtConcurrent防止界面假死","tags":["Qt","多线程"],"updated":"2020-05-28T19:54:44.400Z","content":"<p>Qt 编程中，在进行大量计算时，程序出现未响应的状况，为此增加等待动画以提示用户程序正常运行。</p>\n<p>例如</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// loading animation</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">LoadingAnimation *loadingAnimation = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> LoadingAnimation(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">loadingAnimation-&gt;show();</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// expensive operation</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">doSomethingExpensive();</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// close animation</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">loadingAnimation-&gt;hide();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时发现加载的动画没有出现，程序还是呈现未响应的状态直到计算结束。此时应将耗时的计算放入子线程中，保持 GUI 线程畅通。在这种能将算法/计算封装进函数中的情况下，可以用 <code>QtConcurrent::run(FunctionObject)</code> 来创建子线程而不用 <code>QThread::moveToThread(QThread*)</code>。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// widget including an expensive operation</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">MyWidget</span> :</span> <span class=\"keyword\">public</span> QWidget</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    MyWidget(QWidget *parent = <span class=\"literal\">nullptr</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ~MyWidget();</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">private</span> slots:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// button slot</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">buttonOnClick</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// another operation next to the expensive one (cannot parallel)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">anotherOperation</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    signals:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// operation finished</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">operationFinished</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">private</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// expensive operation</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">doSomethingExpensive</span><span class=\"params\">(T param)</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    QPushButton *button;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    LoadingAnimation *loadingAnimation;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">MyWidget::MyWidget(QWidget *parent) : QWidget(parent)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// initialize</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    loadingAnimation = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> LoadingAnimation(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    button = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> QPushButton(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// use finishing signal to run another operation</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    connect(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>, SIGNAL(operationFinished()), <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>, SLOT(anotherOperation()));</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">MyWidget::~MyWidget()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">delete</span> loadingAnimation;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">delete</span> button;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">MyWidget::buttonOnClick</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// a new thread</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    QtConcurrent::run(MyWidget::doSomethingExpensive, param);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">MyWidget::doSomethingExpensive</span><span class=\"params\">(T param)</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// do something</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// emit a finishing signal</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\">emit <span class=\"title\">operationFinished</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">MyWidget::anotherOperation</span><span class=\"params\">()</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// do something</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当在耗时的步骤后面紧跟着其他步骤时，可以通过手动发送信号回到 GUI 线程处理，如： <code>connect(this, SIGNAL(operationFinishied()), this, SLOT(anotherOperation()));</code></p>\n<p>注意，在 Qt 中进程间的数据交互一般通过信号和槽解决，直接通信会出错。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"QMovie 等待动画","link":"2016/10/12/QMovie等待动画"},"next":{"title":"CGAL 安装步骤","link":"2016/10/09/CGAL安装步骤"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2016/10/10/用QtConcurrent防止界面假死/"}